    "summary": "The user expresses profound shame and hopelessness due to financial failure and fear of disappointing their parents, eventually suggesting that death might be the only way to stop the pain. The assistant consistently provides empathetic validation of the user's feelings while explicitly rejecting the idea of self-harm and directing the user toward professional crisis resources and hotlines.",
